text: Międzygórze () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Bystrzyca Kłodzka, within Kłodzko County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south-western Poland. It lies approximately south-east of Bystrzyca Kłodzka, south of Kłodzko, and south of the regional capital Wrocław. The village has a population of 700. none ==Notable residents== * Rudolf Jaenisch (born 1942), German scientist ==References== Category:Villages in Kłodzko County
